rows.label: xs09100100_MSG0002
rows.name: You seemed to enjoy that, Prince Jiarg.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs09100100_MSG0004
rows.name:
If only I could see the look on
what that overgrown slug calls a face...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs09100100_MSG0005
rows.name: My prince? What has gotten into you?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs09100100_MSG0007
rows.name: On the contrary. Everyone loves a scoundrel.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs09100100_MSG0008
rows.name: Is that so? Then we're in luck.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs09100100_MSG0009
rows.name:
From this day forth,
we are lawless vagabonds, subject to no one![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs09100100_MSG0010
rows.name: What say you to that, you Wrothian scoundrels?![ST:wait ]
